home to work with either model. If the thermostat determines

00:00:13.980 --> 00:00:16.260
how hot the heater is, then the first answer

00:00:16.260 --> 00:00:19.530
is correct. you know, set it high first. That'll

00:00:19.530 --> 00:00:21.830
get you to the correct temperature as quickly as

00:00:21.830 --> 00:00:25.920
possible. But, you know, that's not how most homes work.

00:00:25.920 --> 00:00:29.100
