00:00:34.670 --> 00:00:37.420
control, all the way one way or all the way

00:00:37.420 --> 00:00:40.870
the other. The thermostat turns the heat on full

00:00:40.870 --> 00:00:43.760
until it reaches the set point, at which point it

00:00:43.760 --> 00:00:47.590
