00:00:47.590 --> 00:00:51.330
do any good. It doesn't speed things up and worse,

00:00:51.330 --> 00:00:55.230
if you forget to turn it back, well the house keeps getting hotter and

00:00:55.230 --> 00:00:57.970
hotter and hotter. Wasting energy and maybe

